      <title>诺沃格拉茨称，随着特朗普获胜，Galaxy 迎来今年最大交易日</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/novogratz-says-galaxy-registers-biggest-trading-day-of-the-year-as-trump-wins</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Galaxy Digital 的亿万富翁创始人迈克尔·诺沃格拉茨表示，随着唐纳德·特朗普在美国总统竞选中获胜，人们对加密货币的兴趣激增，这家数字资产公司周三创下了今年最大的交易日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/novogratz-says-galaxy-registers-biggest-trading-day-of-the-year-as-trump-wins</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 15:34:16 GMT</pubDate>
